sequenceDiagram
    participant AI as AI Assistant
    participant Claude as Claude Code
    participant Hook as validate-arc-filename.mjs
    participant Config as config/doc-types.mjs
    participant FS as File System

    AI->>Claude: Write(path, content)
    Claude->>Hook: PreToolUse event (stdin JSON)
    Hook->>Hook: Parse stdin input
    Hook->>Hook: Extract filename from path
    
    alt Filename is ARC-* pattern
        Hook->>Hook: extractDocType(filename)
        Hook->>Hook: extractProjectId(filename)
        Hook->>Hook: extractVersion(filename)
        Hook->>Config: Check MULTI_INSTANCE_TYPES
        Hook->>Config: Check SUBDIR_MAP
        
        alt Multi-instance type
            Hook->>FS: Scan subdirectory for existing files
            Hook->>Hook: Determine next sequence number
            Hook->>Hook: Build corrected path with sequence
        else Single-instance type
            Hook->>Hook: Build corrected path (project root)
        end
        
        Hook->>Hook: Apply zero-padding (001)
        Hook->>Hook: Normalize version (1.0)
        Hook->>Claude: Return corrected path via stdout JSON
    else Not ARC-* pattern
        Hook->>Claude: Allow original path
    end
    
    Claude->>FS: Write to corrected path
    Claude->>AI: Return success
